// Defines the SIDELOAD compilation condition for the unsigned sideload IPA built in CI.
// Passed to xcodebuild via -xcconfig only by the sideload workflow; the App Store /
// TestFlight build never references it, so its binary is unaffected.
//
// $(inherited) is required: an xcconfig override of SWIFT_ACTIVE_COMPILATION_CONDITIONS
// replaces the value, which would otherwise wipe the Debug config's DEBUG condition.
SWIFT_ACTIVE_COMPILATION_CONDITIONS = $(inherited) SIDELOAD
